title: Azerbaijan Consumer Price Index Cpi
description: Consumer Price Index CPI in Azerbaijan increased to 201.40 points in September from 195.30 points in August of 2022. Consumer Price Index CPI in Azerbaijan averaged 138.78 points from 2011 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 201.40 points in September of 2022 and a record low of 105.30 points in January of 2011. This page provides - Azerbaijan Consumer Price Index Cpi- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: The State Statistical Committee of the Republic of Azerbaijan
